description: LifeClean International AB engages in the production, marketing, and sale of disinfectant products. The company is headquartered in Uddevalla, Vastra Gotalands. The company went IPO on 2020-10-01. The firm conduct research, production, marketing and sales of disinfectant products. The Company’s product LifeClean Disinfection is to be used against spores, viruses, bacteria, fungi, parasites and biofilm, without leaving residual products and preventing the development of multi-resistant organisms.
naics: Soap, Cleaning Compound, and Toilet Preparation Manufacturing
